<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>173</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Thiang Thlarau, na ceunak kha, Keimah lung chungah ceu tuah, A muihnak
 kha lohter law, Ka muihnak hi ceuter ko.

[V2]
 Thiang Thlarau, na thawnnak in, Ka lung chung kha thianter tuah,
 Sualnak nih caan sau tuk in, Ka lung chung kha a pen cang.

[V3]
 Thiang Thlarau, na lawmhnak in, Ka lungthin chung khahter tuah,
 Sifahnak vialte tianter, Ngaihchiatnak lung damter ko.

[V4]
 Thiang Thlarau, Pathian Thlarau, Ka lungthin chungah um tuah, Siasal
 biaknak hlonh dih law, Nangmah lawng ka Bawi si ko.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<title>THIANG THLARAU, NA CEUNAK HE CH173</title>
</song>